;
;       Name: ECMOF
;       Type: Subroutine
;   Category: Sound
;    Summary: Switch off the E.C.M.
;
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
;
; Switch the E.C.M. off, turn off the dashboard bulb and make the sound of the
; E.C.M. switching off).
;
; ******************************************************************************

.ECMOF

